    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北京以谷歌调查回击特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/china-probes-google-moments-after-trump-s-tariffs-enter-effect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国针对唐纳德·特朗普发起的贸易战关税进行了反击，针对少数美国公司并对部分美国商品征收关税，此举似乎是为了避免世界两大经济体之间的紧张局势升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/china-probes-google-moments-after-trump-s-tariffs-enter-effect</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 05:05:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普发起中美贸易战 黄金价格稳定在历史高位附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-tariff-confusion-aids-haven-bids</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国征收 10% 的关税后，金价稳定在历史高位附近，提振了避险需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-tariff-confusion-aids-haven-bids</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 00:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
